{"tid":1495500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"監警會張華峰護警！稱不展示警員編號為保執法「無後顧之憂」","createTime":"2019-08-22T05:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T14:51:22.000Z","uid":213379,"like":12,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2dda127924177c98c73430a39b7db3ffdcb141f0","tid":1495500,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"張華峰相信監警會涉及7月2日前事件的中期報告可以如期在半年內提交。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n監警會主動審視近期的大型公眾活動，監警會副主席張華峰今早出席港台節目時，指監警會現時未開始審議接獲的174宗投訴個案，但稱監警會處理反修例風波相關警方投訴的進度良好，相信涉及7月2日前事件的中期報告可以如期在半年內提交。他認為監警會現時委員人數仍足以應付目前個案，是否需要增加委員或行政人手應由特首及監警會主席決定，又稱不論現時監警會成員政治立場如何，相信每個人都會按法律公平處理投訴個案。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【逆權運動】80後工程師成立工程思政 逼退業界的「白色恐怖」<br />\n<br />\n張華峰說，警方會向監警會提供多少資料有既定政策，強調雙方溝通很重要，亦相信每名監警會委員都是公平公正及認真對待每宗個案，他們在開會有積極發言。對於警員尤其速龍小隊近月經常執勤時都不展示警員編號，令市民投訴無門，張則為其辯解稱不展示編號可以避免被起底等情況發生，令警員在執法時無後顧之憂，又指警方在鎮壓騷亂時，仍要面對各種限制並不合理。被問到這情況下，示威者如何識別警員資料以作投訴，張華峰認為應由投訴警察課處理。張華峰說，警方在處理騷動時使用的武力是否過分，要視乎對方的反應如何，反問當警方執行社會穩定的任務是否要限制他們使用武力的程度，認為當時應由警員作判斷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190822/59959415?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190822%2F59959415%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGISq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=a552f326\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190822%2F59959415%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=2c2865e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190822/59959415?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你啦 個個無Number你又唔洗做野 <br />\n仲要你個監警會做乜呀 ？</span></span>"},{"pid":"181e899fc7ae2d839a7c419b01adbb9cb19a328f","tid":1495500,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:50:44.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU，而家搭車犯法呀?</strong></span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrRtRqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrRtRqw.jpg&h=a938cd9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTCkHxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTCkHxb.jpg&h=73ff0599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00prC5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00prC5w.jpg&h=ccabd632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJckHxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJckHxb.jpg&h=e84b0cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3bJFtJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3bJFtJ.jpg&h=400310ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mzORrS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mzORrS.jpg&h=e1aa2d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvSwHez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvSwHez.png&h=660b03dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84b1bc8db3b92a096767414e505494d99726d9de","tid":1495500,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:50: